<!-- HERO -->
<div class="layout">
  <section class="hero">
    <div class="kicker">Dr. Deas Music Suite</div>
    <h1>Three tools.<br><span class="aa">Two generations.</span><br><span class="ab">Build yours.</span></h1>
    <p class="lede">
      A drum machine, a pattern library, and a chord synthesizer — deployed with
      <a href="https://links.vibes.diy/CLI">npx vibes-diy</a>.
      Clone any of them, or <strong>build fresh</strong> from the specs below.
