<!-- THE ORIGINALS -->
<div class="layout">
  <div class="section-wrap">
    <div class="section-head">
      <div class="section-kicker sk-amber">01 — Original run</div>
      <h2>The Originals</h2>
      <p>Three instruments deployed from short prompts. Shipped, used, iterated.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="app-grid">

      <!-- Drum Machine -->
      <article class="app-card app-card--orig">
        <div class="card-meta">
          <span class="card-badge badge-orig">Original</span>
          <span class="card-num">01 / 03</span>
        </div>
        <div class="card-shot">
          <img
            src="https://excited-wombat-4753--og.prod-v2.vibesdiy.net/screenshot.jpg"
            alt="Dr. Deas Drum Machine"
            onerror="this.onerror=null; this.src='{{@root.assetPrefix}}images/og-preview.png';"
          />
        </div>
        <div class="card-body">
          <h3 class="card-title">Dr. Deas Drum Machine</h3>
          <p class="card-tagline">Style-generated patterns. Custom samples. Solo and mute.</p>
          <p class="card-desc">Describe your beat — dark trap, four-on-the-floor, reggaeton break — and all 8 tracks fill in at once. Adjust BPM, save patterns by name, solo and mute for mixing.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card-actions">
          <a href="https://vibes.diy/vibe/og/excited-wombat-4753" class="btn btn-join">Join</a>
          <a href="https://vibes.diy/remix/og/excited-wombat-4753?skipChat=true" class="btn btn-clone">Clone</a>
          <a href="https://vibes.diy/remix/og/excited-wombat-4753" class="btn btn-remix">Remix</a>
        </div>
        <p class="card-fork">Want a 12-track version with custom Latin percussion voices, or a 4-track minimal techno sequencer? Clone it and rewrite the track list and sound synthesis.</p>
        <div class="prompt-block">
          <div class="prompt-header">
            <span class="prompt-label">// build fresh →</span>
            <button class="copy-btn" onclick="copyFromBlock(this)">Copy</button>
          </div>
          <pre class="prompt-text">Step sequencer drum machine, 8 tracks, BPM control. AI beat generator: describe style and genre, fills all tracks. Solo, mute, save patterns by name.</pre>
        </div>
      </article>

      <!-- Pattern Saver -->
      <article class="app-card app-card--orig">
        <div class="card-meta">
          <span class="card-badge badge-orig">Original</span>
          <span class="card-num">02 / 03</span>
        </div>
        <div class="card-shot">
          <img
            src="https://mass-bug-7792--og.prod-v2.vibesdiy.net/screenshot.jpg"
            alt="Dr. Deas Pattern Saver"
            onerror="this.onerror=null; this.src='{{@root.assetPrefix}}images/og-preview.png';"
          />
        </div>
        <div class="card-body">
          <h3 class="card-title">Dr. Deas Pattern Saver</h3>
          <p class="card-tagline">Instrument-first workflow. LEVEL, TUNE, DECAY per track.</p>
          <p class="card-desc">Select a drum voice, program 16 steps, dial in the feel. LEVEL, TUNE, and DECAY controls per instrument. Pattern generator and demo patterns included.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card-actions">
