          <h3 class="card-title">Drum Studio</h3>
          <p class="card-tagline">Pattern chains. Tube warmth. Dynamics compression.</p>
          <p class="card-desc">Lookahead scheduler, DynamicsCompressor + WaveShaper tube warmth on the master bus. 16-step grid grouped by beat, per-track volume and tune.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card-actions">
          <a href="https://vibes.diy/vibe/og/drum-studio" class="btn btn-join">Join</a>
          <a href="https://vibes.diy/remix/og/drum-studio?skipChat=true" class="btn btn-clone">Clone</a>
          <a href="https://vibes.diy/remix/og/drum-studio" class="btn btn-remix">Remix</a>
        </div>
        <p class="card-fork">You need a polyrhythm mode where each track can run its own step count independently. Clone it and add a per-track length selector alongside the BPM control.</p>
        <div class="prompt-block">
